- [ ] T041 [P] Setup React Query configuration in frontend/src/app/providers.tsx
- [ ] T042 [P] Create reusable UI components (Button, Input, Card, Loading) in frontend/src/components/ui/

**Checkpoint**: ‚úÖ Foundation ready - user story implementation can now begin in parallel

