## Phase 3: User Story 1 - Basic Text Generation and Q&A (Priority: P1) üéØ MVP

**Goal**: Enable employees to submit text queries and receive LLM-generated responses with conversational context

**Independent Test**: Can test without any other user story complete. Submit query ‚Üí receive response ‚Üí verify Korean quality.

### Backend Implementation

- [ ] T043 [US1] Implement conversation context management service in backend/app/services/context_service.py (10-message window, 2048 token limit, FIFO)
- [ ] T044 [US1] Implement chat endpoint POST /api/v1/chat with streaming support in backend/app/api/v1/chat.py
- [ ] T045 [US1] Implement conversation CRUD endpoints in backend/app/api/v1/conversations.py (create, list, get, delete)
- [ ] T046 [US1] Implement message history endpoint GET /api/v1/conversations/{id}/messages in backend/app/api/v1/conversations.py

### Frontend Implementation

- [ ] T047 [P] [US1] Create chat page layout in frontend/src/app/(user)/chat/page.tsx
- [ ] T048 [P] [US1] Implement ChatInput component with 6 UI states in frontend/src/components/chat/ChatInput.tsx (idle, typing, processing, streaming, completed, error per FR-035)
- [ ] T049 [P] [US1] Implement MessageList component in frontend/src/components/chat/MessageList.tsx
- [ ] T050 [P] [US1] Implement StreamingMessage component with real-time text display in frontend/src/components/chat/StreamingMessage.tsx
- [ ] T051 [US1] Integrate chat API with React Query in frontend/src/app/(user)/chat/page.tsx

### Manual Testing (Per Acceptance Scenarios)

- [ ] T052 [US1] Verify query submission and response generation (<10 seconds per SC-001)
- [ ] T053 [US1] Verify streaming response display works correctly
- [ ] T054 [US1] Verify conversational context maintained across follow-up questions
- [ ] T055 [US1] Test Korean response quality using test script (90% pass rate per SC-004)

