- [ ] T139 [US6] Integrate safety filter warnings into chat interface in frontend/src/app/(user)/chat/page.tsx

### Manual Testing

- [ ] T140 [US6] Test Phase 1 rule-based filter blocks inappropriate keywords (violence, sexual, hate, dangerous)
- [ ] T141 [US6] Test Phase 2 ML filter detects toxic content (95%+ accuracy on test dataset per SC-014)
- [ ] T142 [US6] Test PII masking for Ï£ºÎØºÎì±Î°ùÎ≤àÌò∏, phone, email (100% detection per SC-015)
